ortant; min-height: auto !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">}</span></code></div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">在没有遇到<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">[</span></strong>的时候，系统不会收集，只有遇见[的时候，才算是一个事件，才收集起来。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>参考内容<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/logstash/current/plugins-codecs-multiline.html<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 153); font-size: 14px;\">（3）Kibana安装配置</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255);\">1）kibana的安装：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>[root@elk-node1 ~]# cd /usr/local/src<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>[root@elk-node1 src]# wget https://download.elastic.co/kibana/kibana/kibana-4.3.1-linux-x64.tar.gz<br sty