"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>There is a screen on:<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>15041.pts-0.elk-node1 (Detached)<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>1 Socket in /var/run/screen/S-root.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(204, 255, 255);\">（3）访问kibana：http://112.110.115.10:15601/</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">如下，如果是添加上面设置的java日志收集信息，则在下面填写es-error*；如果是添加上面设置的系统日志信息system*，以此类型(可以从logstash界面看到日志收集项)</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/907596/201611/907596-20161111184157108-1169665374.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 900px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;然后点击上面的Discover，在Discover中查看：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/907596/201611/907596-20161111184459999-1772130220.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 900px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">查看日志登陆，需要点击“Discover”--&gt;&quot;message&quot;,点击它后面的“add”</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(255, 0, 255);\">注意：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 153);\">需要右边查看日志内容时带什么属性，就在左边点击相应属性后面的“add”</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 153);\">如下图，添加了message和path的属性：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/907596/201611/907596-20161111184749499-1028814126.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 900px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/907596/201611/907596-20161111184809264-1464457963.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 900px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这样，右边显示的日志内容的属性就带了message和path</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/907596/201611/907596-20161111184856077-432106611.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 900px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-size: 14px;\">点击右边日志内容属性后面隐藏的&lt;&lt;，就可将内容向前缩进</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/907596/201611/907596-20161111185051061-1158513601.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 900px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"https://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/907596/201611/907596-20161111185141327-802283511.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 900px;\"/></p><p style=